---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="André | Portfólio">
  <div class="mx-auto min-h-screen max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-12 md:px-12 md:py-20 lg:px-24 lg:py-0">
    <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between lg:gap-4">
      <header class="lg:sticky lg:top-0 lg:flex lg:max-h-screen lg:w-1/2 lg:flex-col lg:justify-between lg:py-24">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">
            André
          </h1>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-200 sm:text-xl">
            Estudante de Ciência de Dados e IA | Engenheiro de Software
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-xs leading-normal text-gray-400">
            Desenvolvendo soluções escaláveis e sistemas baseados em dados.
          </p>
          <nav class="nav hidden lg:block mt-16">
            <ul class="w-max">
              <li>
                <a class="group flex items-center py-3 active" href="#sobre">
                  <span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-gray-500 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-white group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-white motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
                  <span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white group-focus-visible:text-white">Sobre</span>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a class="group flex items-center py-3" href="#experiencia">
                  <span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-gray-500 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-white group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-white motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
                  <span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white group-focus-visible:text-white">Experiência</span>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a class="group flex items-center py-3" href="#projetos">
                  <span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-gray-500 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-white group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-white motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
                  <span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white group-focus-visible:text-white">Projetos</span>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <ul class="ml-1 mt-8 flex items-center gap-5">
          <li class="mr-5 text-xs shrink-0">
            <a class="block hover:text-white text-gray-400 transition-colors" href="https://github.com/sschettinii" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              <span class="sr-only">GitHub</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="mr-5 text-xs shrink-0">
            <a class="block hover:text-white text-gray-400 transition-colors" href="hhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/andretomonagaschettini/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </header>

      <main id="content" class="pt-24 lg:w-1/2 lg:py-24">
        <section id="sobre" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24">
          <div class="sticky top-0 z-20 -mx-6 mb-4 w-screen bg-[#111111]/75 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur md:-mx-12 md:px-12 lg:sr-only lg:relative lg:top-auto lg:mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-0 lg:py-0 lg:opacity-0">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-200 lg:sr-only">Sobre</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-400">
              Sou estudante de Ciência de Dados na UEL e atuo como desenvolvedor na TCS. Minha experiência engloba o design de arquiteturas de software voltadas a escalabilidade, assim como a construção de pipelines de dados e de modelos de machine learning, como soluções de manutenção preditiva aplicadas à infraestrutura industrial.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-400">
              Paralelamente ao desenvolvimento corporativo, aplico conceitos técnicos na elaboração de projetos pessoais focados em finanças quantitativas e backtesting de estratégias de investimento em Python, e me dedico ao gerenciamento de sistemas de anotações automatizados.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="experiencia" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24">
          <div class="sticky top-0 z-20 -mx-6 mb-4 w-screen bg-[#111111]/75 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur md:-mx-12 md:px-12 lg:sr-only lg:relative lg:top-auto lg:mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-0 lg:py-0 lg:opacity-0">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-200 lg:sr-only">Experiência</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <ol class="group/list">
              <li class="mb-12">
                <div class="group relative grid pb-1 transition-all sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4 lg:hover:!opacity-100 lg:group-hover/list:opacity-50">
                  <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md transition motion-reduce:transition-none lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block lg:group-hover:bg-gray-800/50 lg:group-hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_0_rgba(148,163,184,0.1)] lg:group-hover:drop-shadow-lg"></div>
                  <header class="z-10 mb-2 mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 sm:col-span-2">2026 — Presente</header>
                  <div class="z-10 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3 class="font-medium leading-snug text-gray-200">
                      <div>
                        <a class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-gray-200 hover:text-white focus-visible:text-white group/link text-base" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                          <span>Developer Trainee · <span class="inline-block">TCS</span></span>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-gray-400">Atuação no desenvolvimento de software, integração de sistemas e aplicação de boas práticas de engenharia no ambiente corporativo.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projetos" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24">
          <div class="sticky top-0 z-20 -mx-6 mb-4 w-screen bg-[#111111]/75 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur md:-mx-12 md:px-12 lg:sr-only lg:relative lg:top-auto lg:mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-0 lg:py-0 lg:opacity-0">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-200 lg:sr-only">Projetos</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <ul class="group/list">
              <li class="mb-12">
                <div class="group relative grid gap-4 pb-1 transition-all sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4 lg:hover:!opacity-100 lg:group-hover/list:opacity-50">
                  <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md transition motion-reduce:transition-none lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block lg:group-hover:bg-gray-800/50 lg:group-hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_0_rgba(148,163,184,0.1)] lg:group-hover:drop-shadow-lg"></div>
                  <div class="z-10 sm:order-2 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3>
                      <a class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-gray-200 hover:text-white focus-visible:text-white group/link text-base" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                        <span>Manutenção Preditiva com Machine Learning</span>
                      </a>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-gray-400">Prova de conceito (PoC) para previsão de falhas em equipamentos industriais. Utilização de dados sintéticos estruturados em banco de dados PostgreSQL e aplicação de modelos de Machine Learning para detecção de anomalias.</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap">
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Python</div></li>
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">PostgreSQL</div></li>
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Machine Learning</div></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="mb-12">
                <div class="group relative grid gap-4 pb-1 transition-all sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4 lg:hover:!opacity-100 lg:group-hover/list:opacity-50">
                  <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md transition motion-reduce:transition-none lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block lg:group-hover:bg-gray-800/50 lg:group-hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_0_rgba(148,163,184,0.1)] lg:group-hover:drop-shadow-lg"></div>
                  <div class="z-10 sm:order-2 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3>
                      <a class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-gray-200 hover:text-white focus-visible:text-white group/link text-base" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                        <span>Gestor Financeiro Automatizado</span>
                      </a>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-gray-400">Ferramenta para categorização de despesas e previsão de hábitos de consumo. Integração via API com múltiplas instituições financeiras para consolidação automatizada dos dados bancários.</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap">
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Python</div></li>
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">API Integration</div></li>
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Data Analysis</div></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="mb-12">
                <div class="group relative grid gap-4 pb-1 transition-all sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4 lg:hover:!opacity-100 lg:group-hover/list:opacity-50">
                  <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md transition motion-reduce:transition-none lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block lg:group-hover:bg-gray-800/50 lg:group-hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_0_rgba(148,163,184,0.1)] lg:group-hover:drop-shadow-lg"></div>
                  <div class="z-10 sm:order-2 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3>
                      <a class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-gray-200 hover:text-white focus-visible:text-white group/link text-base" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                        <span>Backtesting de Estratégia Quantitativa</span>
                      </a>
                    </h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-gray-400">Desenvolvimento de ferramenta para simulação e avaliação histórica da estratégia de investimento Dual Momentum, incorporando análise de performance e risco do portfólio.</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap">
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Python</div></li>
                      <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2"><div class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#1e293b] px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-gray-300">Quant Finance</div></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>